### ============================================================================
### URL Autenticacion (rol receptor electronico)
### Flujo: GET semilla -> firmar con certificado -> POST validarsemilla
### ============================================================================

### 1) Obtener semilla (XML)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/ecf/autenticacion/semilla

### 2) Validar semilla firmada (POST con XML firmado en campo "xml")
###    El consumidor (DGII u otro emisor) debe firmar el XML semilla con su
###    certificado y enviarlo aqui. La respuesta contiene el bearer token.
POST http://localhost:8000/api/ecf/autenticacion/validarsemilla
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----GratexBoundary

------GratexBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="xml"; filename="semilla_firmada.xml"
Content-Type: text/xml

<SemillaModel><valor>VALOR_DE_SEMILLA</valor><fecha>2026-05-07T10:30:00</fecha><Signature>...</Signature></SemillaModel>
------GratexBoundary--

### ============================================================================
### URL Recepcion (otro emisor nos envia un e-CF)
### ============================================================================

### 3) Recibir un e-CF firmado (POST multipart con bearer del paso 2)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/ecf/recepcion
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_DEL_PASO_2
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----GratexBoundary

------GratexBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="xml"; filename="ecf.xml"
Content-Type: text/xml

<ECF>...</ECF>
------GratexBoundary--

### 4) Consultar estado de un e-CF recibido por trackId
GET http://localhost:8000/api/ecf/recepcion/TRACK_ID_DEVUELTO
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_DEL_PASO_2

### 5) Listar e-CF recibidos
GET http://localhost:8000/api/ecf/recepcion?page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_DEL_PASO_2

### ============================================================================
### URL Aprobacion Comercial (un comprador acepta/rechaza un e-CF que emitimos)
### ============================================================================

### 6) Recibir aprobacion comercial firmada
POST http://localhost:8000/api/ecf/aprobacion-comercial
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_DEL_PASO_2
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----GratexBoundary

------GratexBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="xml"; filename="acecf.xml"
Content-Type: text/xml

<ACECF><RNCEmisor>00109122788</RNCEmisor><eNCF>E310000000001</eNCF><RNCComprador>...</RNCComprador><Estado>1</Estado><Signature>...</Signature></ACECF>
------GratexBoundary--
